{"tid":1562370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［千奇唔好］港鐵呼籲切勿在露天鐵路附近燃放孔明燈或攜帶金屬氣球","createTime":"2019-09-12T03:46:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T03:55:17.000Z","uid":48124,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1bbc9674ea03dc57ec4e02f2ef9636a3c86c1510","tid":1562370,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:46:44.000Z","msg":"港鐵指，與政府相關部門檢視近期情況，以及進行風險評估後，決定明天中秋節會按正常服務時間提供列車服務，將不會提供通宵列車服務，所有港鐵車站將按平常服務時間關閉，但因應預期上升的乘客量，部分港鐵路線將由下午三時起加密班次，一些較繁忙的車站將實施特別人流管理措施。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵呼籲市民在慶祝節日時，為鐵路運作安全著想，切勿在鐵路露天路段附近燃放孔明燈或攜帶金屬氣球進入港鐵範圍，以免影響鐵路運作，<span style=\"color: red;\">又指可浮起的LED氣球有燃燒及爆炸的潛在危險，乘客亦不可攜帶這類氣球進入港鐵範圍</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eefadb4445a4582706cd9cb0bc181a330456cf4","tid":1562370,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:46:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"b173e5ee9082ee0e1af4e1e80999d8870cda28de","tid":1562370,"uid":182998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:49:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bdfa005ca48e960fce213832349c680b62e0477c","tid":1562370,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}